<section class="band faq">
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="head"><span class="eyebrow">Questions</span></div>
        <details open><summary>Which tier do I need?</summary><p>Most individual cases are Personal Shield — one person, one phone, every account. Add devices, people, or your home from the add-ons. The Threat Assessment exists to settle this, and its fee comes off whichever tier you choose.</p></details>
        <details><summary>Can I add devices or people later?</summary><p>Yes. Any add-on can be booked with your engagement or afterward, at the same fixed price.</p></details>
        <details><summary>What counts as my "primary device"?</summary><p>Your phone — iOS or Android. It holds the most, so it's the heart of the engagement. A laptop, tablet, or PC is an additional device.</p></details>
        <details><summary>Are there any recurring fees?</summary><p>No — each tier and add-on is one-time, except Annual Watch and the Priority Retainer, which are optional yearly add-ons.</p></details>
        <details><summary>How do I pay, and is it private?</summary><p>Discussed directly and confidentially when you book. Contact is by WhatsApp or Signal only — no forms, no third parties.</p></det